Plugins to checkout:
    https://github.com/machakann/vim-sandwich
        alternative surround

    https://github.com/kana/vim-textobj-user
        -define textobjects
        also:
            https://github.com/bps/vim-textobj-python
            https://github.com/mattn/vim-textobj-url
            https://github.com/sgur/vim-textobj-parameter


    https://github.com/t9md/vim-transform
    https://github.com/inkarkat/vim-TextTransform
        transforming text

    https://github.com/rhysd/devdocs.vim
        -integrate with devdocs.io
    https://github.com/wincent/loupe
        -improved search/replace

    https://github.com/jonmorehouse/vim-flow
        -workflow by running shell commands
    https://github.com/justinmk/vim-gtfo
        -open terminal/finder
    https://github.com/kana/vim-submode
        -define submodes
    https://github.com/ntpeters/vim-better-whitespace
        -trailing whitespace


Others:
    https://github.com/tpope/vim-projectionist
        projections (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jDafvUESbs

    https://github.com/dbakker/vim-projectroot
        Find out which project a file belongs to, easy to use in scripts/mappings

    https://github.com/tpope/vim-dispatch
        Async runner

    https://github.com/kana/vim-textobj-indent OR https://github.com/michaeljsmith/vim-indent-object
        Text objects for indented blocks

    https://github.com/christoomey/vim-sort-motion
        Sort by lines, visual, indentation (requires vim-textobj-indent)

    https://github.com/vimwiki/vimwiki
        Personal Wiki for Vim

    https://github.com/jceb/vim-orgmode ?
        Orgmode

    https://github.com/coderifous/textobj-word-column.vim
        Adds text-objects for word-based columns

    http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=189 OR 
    https://github.com/vim-scripts/VisIncr
        renumbering 
